sources.title: War Dogs (1942) ACE THE WONDER DOG
sources.description:
Stars: Billy Lee, Addison Richards, Bradley Page
Director: S. Roy Luby

When young boy donates his best friend to be trained as an Army war dog, the heroic canine protects a defense plant from saboteurs.

sources.title: War Dogs (1942) Action, Adventure, Drama Full Length Movie
sources.description:
SOUL STIRRING HIT! You'll want to cheer this kid who sends his best pal off to fight for Uncle Sam! 
A young boy donates his pet, a police dog, to the army to be trained as a war dog.

Director: S. Roy Luby
Writers: John Vlahos, Ande Lamb
Stars: Billy Lee, Addison Richards, Bradley Page 
Genres: Action, Adventure, Drama, Romance, War
